[:en] # About The Invisible Man<br>
In this slot machine the classic Universal film from the 1930’s is portrayed – The Invisible Man. The slot is produced in collaboration with Universal Studios and is particularly relevant as the production company recently announced a remake starring none other than Johnny Depp as the main character.</li>
</ul>
<p>The story tells the tale about a professor that discovers a formula that makes him invisible but at the same time turns him into a murderous maniac. With a spooky undertone you spin away with walking wilds to Free Spins followed by two different bonus games. You’ll follow The Invisible Man as he’s sneaking around trying to avoid the police and with sound and music from the original movie together with beautiful 3D animations this video slot is definitely something extra.</p>
<h2 id="game-features">Game features</h2>
<p>The game consists of five wheels with three rows and is packed with special features suck as win both ways, walking wilds with re-spins, Free Spins and two exciting bonus games.</p>
<h3 id="wild-1">Wild</h3>
<p>The wild symbol replaces all other symbols and is a so-called walking wild which means that it travels across the screen from both left and right. As long as a wild is active, every spin that follows is a free re-spin.</p>
<h3 id="free-spins">Free Spins</h3>
<p>Once two walking wilds collide somewhere on the same row you are awarded 10 Free Spins. Note that if you succeed in hitting two wild collisions at the same time the amount of Free Spins is doubled to 20. Whilst in the Free Spins mode the objective is to collect at least eight wild symbols. As soon as a wild has walked across the screen it is saved to the bar in the top of the game. The Invisible Man walks to the left and the police to the right. If you manage to collect at least eight of one kind before the Free Spins are ended you will enter the final bonus game. Since all wilds give you re-spins in every spin the probability of entering the final bonus game is high.</p>
<h3 id="bonus-game">Bonus Game</h3>
<p>In the first bonus game – Griffin’s Rage – you’ll chase the invisible man by playing the exciting pick &amp; click game that awards you with coin wins of different values. In the other bonus game – Police Spins – you’ll follow the police as they surround the invisible man. Here you get three highly valuable Free Spins that are charged with five randomly placed burning wilds and the big wins are a fact.</p>
